    "title": "Thomas Cook India Global Group is Hiring: Guest Relations Manager (Lead)",
    "description": "Thomas Cook India Global Group invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Guest Relations Manager at our Tiruchirappalli location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Thomas Cook India Global Group:\nThomas Cook India Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Flexible working hours\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Thomas Cook India Global Group!",
